Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:21.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:21.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飛躍吧！盡你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸騰有如泉湧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:28.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:28.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我們的週遭佈滿陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:32.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:32.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用淚水洗去血染的污點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:35.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:35.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}讓雙眼避開所有的蠱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之風會引領我們向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:59.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:59.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波濤洶湧的世界裡找尋指引
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:03.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
