Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背騎的身影穿梭其間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我們需要的是你們的共鳴
